  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: cbccbe1d123a55e4e89fbc28b5834c35, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueTrigger
  dialogue:
    sentences:
    - ???. Oh hello there, young man...
    - ???. It seems like you're lost, aren't you?
    - ???. Well, I know that you have the time rewinding ability...
    - ???. And it feels great, doesn't it?
    - ???. But I will have to stop you right there...
    - '???. You see, the ability is dangerous itself... '
    - '???. I''ve seen how your friend died, not because I was hiding there '
    - '???. But because I just rewinded in time... '
    - ???. I also see that you will again fall into a pit that you didn't hope for
    - ???. Listen, this power...
    - ???. It's capable of disintegrating people who use it too much...
    - '???. I lost some of my organs because of it... '
    - '???. I have electronics inside that keep me alive '
    - '???. I don''t want you to also end up like me... '
    - ???. And I want you to give the ability to the collector
    - ???. Why didn't I give it back? It's because i was too carried away by the
      ability So much that i was too late to give it back
    - ???. and after that, the real effects started setting in...
    - ???. So, find the ability collector, and give the ability back, before it's
      too late...
